Cost-effectiveness analysis of the introduction of S-1 therapy for first-line 
metastatic breast cancer treatment in Japan: results from the randomized phase 
III SELECT BC trial.

Shiroiwa T(1), Fukuda T(2), Shimozuma K(3), Mouri M(4), Hagiwara Y(5), Kawahara 
T(5)(6), Ohsumi S(7), Hozumi Y(8)(9), Sagara Y(10), Ohashi Y(11), Mukai H(12).

