Nations within a nation: variations in epidemiological transition across the 
states of India, 1990-2016 in the Global Burden of Disease Study.

India State-Level Disease Burden Initiative Collaborators.

Collaborators: Dandona L, Dandona R, Kumar GA, Shukla DK, Paul VK, Balakrishnan 
